**************** TRANS ******************
**      transform data files            **
** Copyright        Kristjan Haule      **
** Version 2.1            22.9.2011     **
** modified version by Adriano Amaricci **
******************************************

Usage:

[... |] /Users/amaricci/.scripts/trans f1(#1, #2, ...), [f2(#1, #2, ...)] [file1 file2 ...]

Example1: cat file | /Users/amaricci/.scripts/trans #1 #3-#2 'tan(#4)'

Example2: /Users/amaricci/.scripts/trans #1, #2-#1, #3/#1 file1

note: check your shell passes special characters to /Users/amaricci/.scripts/trans!
      characters like \,$,# need a double-quote or slash!

